s and Maschke's\nTheorem, an important result from the representation theory of finite groups.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Feb 2019 17:01:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 27 Aug 2019 15:10:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-28"}
