of models with gauged L_mu - L_tau\nthat can explain the (g-2)_mu anomaly could be covered almost entirely. As a\nbyproduct, a new Monte Carlo tool to generate neutrino trident events is made\npublicly available.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Feb 2019 19:06:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 7 Jan 2020 11:14:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-08"}
