n rates, obtained from the Kennicutt-schmidt scalling\nrelation, are in the range 1-260$\\times$ 10$^{-3}$ M$_{\\odot}$ yr$^{-1}$. But\nthe gas will also - at least in part - be ejected in the form of the observed\notflows.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Feb 2019 20:38:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 19 Mar 2019 17:25:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-27"}
