 our theory is powerful to predict the magnetic\nproperties, which makes it possible to design new high Curie temperature\ntwo-dimensional semiconducting ferromagnets with polyvalent anion materials.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Feb 2019 05:23:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-04"}
