label size and distance-label size in sparse graphs may be\n$\\Theta(\\frac{n}{2^{(\\log n)^c}})$ for some $0<c < 1$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Feb 2019 13:57:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 23 May 2019 20:16:04 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 21 Jun 2019 18:28:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-25"}
